OL,3,CRetailers urged to suspend sales of
OL,4,Cdisposable BBQs during extreme heat
OL,6,FRetailers in Dorset are being urged to
OL,7,Fsuspend sales of disposable BBQs
OL,8,Famidst growing wildfire fears during
OL,9,Fthe latest spell of extreme heat.
OL,11,FDorset Council and Litter Free Dorset
OL,12,Fsay it would help protect the county's
OL,13,Fcountryside, heathlands, coast and
OL,14,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
