OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783696745
OL,3,CRetailers urged to suspend sales of
OL,4,Cdisposable BBQs during extreme heat
OL,6,FDorset's landscapes include
OL,7,Finternationally important heathlands,
OL,8,Fnature reserves, farmland and coastal
OL,9,Fhabitats - which can become
OL,10,Fparticularly vulnerable during
OL,11,Fprolonged periods of hot, dry weather.
OL,13,FThe council says even a single spark
OL,14,For lingering ember can cause
OL,15,Fsignificant damage to wildlife
OL,16,Fhabitats, threaten nearby properties,
OL,17,Fand put lives at risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783696745
OL,3,CRetailers urged to suspend sales of
OL,4,Cdisposable BBQs during extreme heat
OL,6,FThe authority said that with the
OL,7,Frecent period of extreme heat and
OL,8,Fanother on the way this week, it is
OL,9,Fcrucial that this risk is reduced
OL,10,Fwherever possible.
OL,12,FCouncillor Nick Ireland, Dorset
OL,13,FCouncil Leader, said: "Dorset is home
OL,14,Fto some of the country's most
OL,15,Ftreasured landscapes and wildlife
OL,16,Fhabitats. During periods of extreme
OL,17,Fheat, the risk of wildfire increases
OL,18,Fsignificantly, and we all have a role
OL,19,Fto play in reducing that risk."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783696745
OL,3,CRetailers urged to suspend sales of
OL,4,Cdisposable BBQs during extreme heat
OL,6,F"We are asking those retailers who
OL,7,Fstill choose to sell disposable
OL,8,Fbarbecues to do so responsibly by
OL,9,Ffollowing the British Retail
OL,10,FConsortium's voluntary guidelines and
OL,11,Ftemporarily pausing sales when
OL,12,Fconditions are particularly dangerous.
OL,13,FThis simple action could help prevent
OL,14,Fdevastating fires and protect Dorset's
OL,15,Fenvironment, residents and visitors."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783696745
OL,3,CRetailers urged to suspend sales of
OL,4,Cdisposable BBQs during extreme heat
OL,6,FEmma Teasdale, Litter Free Dorset
OL,7,FCoordinator, said: "Major retailers
OL,8,Fassure us that they follow the BRC
OL,9,Fguidelines, but last month we saw
OL,10,Famber and red extreme heat warnings
OL,11,Fissued by the Met Office, and
OL,12,Fretailers continued to sell disposable
OL,13,Fbarbecues that are clearly a fire
OL,14,Frisk. We are simply asking them to
OL,15,Ffollow the voluntary guidelines they
OL,16,Fhave already agreed to."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783696745
OL,3,CRetailers urged to suspend sales of
OL,4,Cdisposable BBQs during extreme heat
OL,6,F"With the Fire Severity Index at Very
OL,7,FHigh across much of Dorset ` and
OL,8,Ffurther heat warnings being issued for
OL,9,Fthe coming days ` this is no more than
OL,10,Fwhat we should expect from responsible
OL,11,Fretailers."
OL,13,F"By working together, retailers,
OL,14,Fresidents and visitors can help reduce
OL,15,Ffire risk and ensure everyone enjoys
OL,16,FDorset's beautiful outdoor spaces
OL,17,Fsafely."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
